N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 22.14 - Bulk tank unit

State Regulations

Bulk tank unit means a bulk tank unit as established
pursuant to section
20.25
of this Title. Pool milk
received from a producer by a dealer shall be deemed to have been received at a
bulk tank unit if such dealer is a handler as defined in section
20.7
of this
